    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to vcs_versioning Module</title>

      <para>
        <application>vcs_versioning</application> provides essential
        functionality for setuptools_scm that allows that module to properly
        set version control metadata.
      </para>

      &lfs130_checked;

